member.name: T:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.LocationTypeRequest
member.summary: Location Type.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.LocationTypeRequest.Rooftop
member.summary: Indicates that the returned result is a precise geocode for which we have location information accurate down to street address precision.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.LocationTypeRequest.Range_Interpolated
member.summary: Indicates that the returned result reflects an approximation (usually on a road) interpolated between two precise points (such as intersections). Interpolated results are generally returned when rooftop geocodes are unavailable for a street address.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.LocationTypeRequest.Geometric_Center
member.summary: Indicates that the returned result is the geometric center of a result such as a polyline (for example, a street) or polygon (region).

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.LocationTypeRequest.Approximate
member.summary: Indicates that the returned result is approximate.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Street_Address
member.summary: Indicates a precise street address.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Route
member.summary: Indicates a named route (such as "US 101").

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Intersection
member.summary: Indicates a major intersection, usually of two major roads.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Political
member.summary: Indicates a political entity. Usually, this type indicates a polygon of some civil administration.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Country
member.summary: Indicates the national political entity, and is typically the highest order type returned by the Geocoder.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Administrative_Area_Level_1
member.summary: Indicates a first-order civil entity below the country level. Within the United States, these administrative levels are states. Not all nations exhibit these administrative levels.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Administrative_Area_Level_2
member.summary: Indicates a second-order civil entity below the country level. Within the United States, these administrative levels are counties. Not all nations exhibit these administrative levels.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Administrative_Area_Level_3
member.summary: Indicates a third-order civil entity below the country level. This type indicates a minor civil division. Not all nations exhibit these administrative levels.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Administrative_Area_Level_4
member.summary: Indicates a fourth-order civil entity below the country level. This type indicates a minor civil division. Not all nations exhibit these administrative levels.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Administrative_Area_Level_5
member.summary: Indicates a fifth-order civil entity below the country level. This type indicates a minor civil division. Not all nations exhibit these administrative levels.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Administrative_Area_Level_6
member.summary: Indicates a sixth-order civil entity below the country level. This type indicates a minor civil division. Not all nations exhibit these administrative levels.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Administrative_Area_Level_7
member.summary: Indicates a seventh-order civil entity below the country level. This type indicates a minor civil division. Not all nations exhibit these administrative levels.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Colloquial_Area
member.summary: Indicates a commonly-used alternative name for the entity.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Locality
member.summary: Indicates an incorporated city or town political entity.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Sublocality
member.summary: locality.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Neighborhood
member.summary: Indicates a named neighborhood.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Premise
member.summary: Indicates a named location, usually a building or collection of buildings with a common name.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Subpremise
member.summary: Indicates a first-order entity below a named location, usually a singular building within a collection of buildings with a common name.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Plus_Code
member.summary:
Indicates an encoded location reference, derived from latitude and longitude.
Plus codes can be used as a replacement for street addresses in places where they do not exist (where buildings are not numbered or streets are not named).
See for details.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Postal_Code
member.summary: Indicates a postal code as used to address postal mail within the country.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Natural_Feature
member.summary: Indicates a prominent natural feature.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Airport
member.summary: Airport.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Park
member.summary: Park.

member.name: F:JordiAragon.ToDos.Infrastructure.Geolocation.GoogleMaps.Geocode.Requests.ResultTypeRequest.Point_Of_Interest
member.summary: Indicates a named point of interest. Typically, these "POI"s are prominent local entities that don't easily fit in another category such as "Empire State Building" or "Statue of Liberty".
